{
  "page": "Meralyn",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\"><img alt=\"Braavos.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/50px-Braavos.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/75px-Braavos.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/100px-Braavos.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Meralyn</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\"><img alt=\"Braavos.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/50px-Braavos.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/75px-Braavos.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/100px-Braavos.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nMerry</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Happy_Port\" title=\"Happy Port\">Happy Port</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavosi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Meralyn</b>, more commonly called <b>Merry</b>, is the proprietor of the <a href=\"/index.php/Happy_Port\" title=\"Happy Port\">Happy Port</a>, a brothel near <a href=\"/index.php/Ragman%27s_Harbor\" title=\"Ragman&#39;s Harbor\">Ragman's Harbor</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes_by_Meralyn\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes by Meralyn</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes_about_Meralyn\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes about Meralyn</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Meralyn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Meralyn is an older woman<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> said to have a good heart, and she claims to have the largest breasts in <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Merry charges three times more for young <a href=\"/index.php/Lanna\" title=\"Lanna\">Lanna</a> than her other <a href=\"/index.php/Prostitutes\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Prostitutes\">prostitutes</a>. She believes that <a href=\"/index.php/Mummers\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Mummers\">mummers</a> make better priests than actual priests.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Meralyn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Meralyn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Meralyn buys a dozen oysters from Cat (<a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a>) whenever Cat passes by the <a href=\"/index.php/Happy_Port\" title=\"Happy Port\">Happy Port</a>, and she shares them with her girls. Merry allows <a href=\"/index.php/Dareon\" title=\"Dareon\">Dareon</a> to sing to her girls.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When <a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Tarly\" title=\"Samwell Tarly\">Samwell Tarly</a> visits the Happy Port in search of Dareon, Merry is turning <a href=\"/index.php/Tiles\" title=\"Tiles\">tiles</a> with a massive <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Islander</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Xhondo_Dhoru\" title=\"Xhondo Dhoru\">Xhondo Dhoru</a>. The proprietor has Sam tossed into the nearby canal after he punches the singer.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Meralyn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Now serving the <a href=\"/index.php/House_of_Black_and_White\" title=\"House of Black and White\">House of Black and White</a> as a blind girl, Arya fondly recalls Merry and the Happy Port.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_by_Meralyn\">Quotes by Meralyn</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Meralyn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes by Meralyn\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The boys unload the ships, and my girls unload the lads who sail them.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Meralyn to <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Cat</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_about_Meralyn\">Quotes about Meralyn</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Meralyn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes about Meralyn\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Meralyn is her true name, but everyone calls her Merry, and she is.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Cat</a> to a sailor</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Meralyn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\">1.5</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_34\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 34\">Chapter 34</a>, Cat Of The Canals.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_26\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 26\">Chapter 26</a>, Samwell III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_45\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 45\">Chapter 45</a>, The Blind Girl.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403183019\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.090 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.277 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1172/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10796/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 8404/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 785/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3082/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.34 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  264.681      1 -total\n 92.32%  244.358      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 91.51%  242.202      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.08%   29.338     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  6.17%   16.334      9 Template:Ref\n  5.43%   14.380      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  3.86%   10.205      9 Template:Ref/core\n  1.38%    3.645      2 Template:Quote\n  0.89%    2.350      1 Template:References\n  0.38%    1.005      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:6518-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403183018 and revision id 287209\n -->\n",
